fields.label: Black Marine Snaps
fields.content: BLACK Marine Snaps - $15 per pack of 10 with black buttons and screw studs. Each order includes one Economy Tool, but we highly recommend ordering the optional Industrial Snap Tool below—it’s much easier to use!

fields.label: White Marine Snaps
fields.content: WHITE Marine Snaps - $15 per pack of 10 with black buttons and screw studs. Each order includes one Economy Tool, but we highly recommend ordering the optional Industrial Snap Tool below—it’s much easier to use!

fields.label: Clear Marine Snaps
fields.content: CLEAR Adhesive Marine Snaps - $15 for a set of 5. These little neoprene doo-dads are pricey but very useful! They work for surfaces you don’t want to (or can’t) screw into, including tile, concrete, smooth brick, metal, and vinyl surfaces. They are not suitable for rough surfaces like stucco, HardiPlank®, or sandstone.

fields.label: White Adhesive Marine Snaps
fields.content: WHITE Adhesive Marine Snaps - $15 per 5 hard plastic snaps. Slightly more durable than the neoprene clear version. Blends better with white trim and concrete (NOT Stucco, sandstone, or Hardiplank). We include screw studs just in case you need an alternative.

fields.label: Black Adhesive Marine Snaps
fields.content: BLACK Adhesive Marine Snaps - $15 per 5 hard plastic snaps. Match dark surfaces and look good on brick. Slightly more durable than the neoprene clear version (NOT Stucco, sandstone, or Hardiplank). We include screw studs just in case you need an alternative.
